metadata.name: ZOM ALPHA PASS
metadata.description: Ownership of the Zom Alpha Pass grants you access to our high-end ZOM NFT Alpha Discord channel that includes some of the industry's most important information circulating the stock market, NFT, and crypto spaces. There are also many other benefits of owning a Zom Alpha Pass, from experts confirming whitelist access for future projects to free mints we think have upside potential. A solid team of elite degens with solid information from high end relationships and other sources are always in our channels, answering questions and providing information. In total only 250 passes will be available for mint. Owning a Zom Alpha Pass is buying into a community where you are given all the info needed to have success in the stock market, NFT, and crypto spaces. & more!
